OL,3,CFormer Scottish rugby star appears in
OL,4,Ccourt for stalking and abuse charges
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,7,FHogg has appeared in court facing
OL,8,Fcharges of stalking and abuse.
OL,10,FHe is accused of "engaging in a course
OL,11,Fof behaviour which was abusive" as
OL,12,Fwell as a stalking charge.
OL,14,FThe 31-year-old also faces a charge of
OL,15,Ffailing to comply with an undertaking.
OL,17,FHe pleaded not guilty to all three
OL,18,Fcharges when he appeared in front of a
OL,19,Fjudge at Jedburgh Sheriff Court today.
